  "body": "Type: Bug\r\n\r\nSummary: Text wrapped up in asterisks is not displayed with bold font style in 1-1 chat and public chats for iOS.\r\nIt's all fine for Android.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nText in message bubble wrapped up in asterisks displayed with bold font style in 1-1 and public chats on iOS\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\n\r\nText in message bubble wrapped up in asterisks is not displayed with bold font style in 1-1 and public chats on iOS\r\n\r\nSee screens from 1-1 chat of Android user and iOS user:\r\n\r\niOS screen:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"512\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/47086564-8cef1580-d222-11e8-9df1-cc7781e7937f.png\">\r\n\r\nAnd same chat on Android screen (where it's all fine):\r\n\r\n<img width=\"512\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/47086611-a8f2b700-d222-11e8-967c-a3c67a706c73.png\">\r\n\r\n**Reproduction**\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Start 1-1 chat with any contact\r\n3. Send text message wrapped up in asterisks (e.g. *bold*)\r\n4. Check if the text in message bubble with bold font style\r\n\r\n**Additional Information**\r\n\r\nStatus version: Release 0.9.30 (10755) - a nightly from 17 Oct 2018\r\nTested on iOS 12.0.1\r\nA previous issue - https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/3180",
